<p>
  <em>Optics Express</em> reports on scientific and technology innovations in all aspects of optics and photonics. The bi-weekly journal provides rapid publication of original, peer-reviewed papers. It is published by Optica Publishing Group and led by Editor-in-Chief James Leger of the University of Minnesota, USA. Optics Express is an open-access journal and is available at no cost to readers online.  For more information, visit <a href="https://opg.optica.org/oe/home.cfm"><em>Optics Express</em></a>.
</p>
 




  
  
  
  
  
  
  
